            {
              "code": "Self",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " passed to the body closure is isolated, meaning that the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "closure can be used to call non-distributed functions, or even access actor",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "state.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When the actor is remote, the closure won’t be executed and this function will return nil.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
